Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.78,0:25:29.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}まどろみの約束
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.90,0:24:10.40,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}今夜與君愛夢相會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.64,0:24:14.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}務必覓得
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.58,0:24:19.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}微眠之約
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.14,0:24:40.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}萌生此等愜意  實乃徒增彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.96,0:24:51.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}予君之意  君不知乎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.33,0:24:57.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}察其目光  未縈他意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.79,0:25:02.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}宛如待友  毫無二致
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.24,0:25:08.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}許願星逝於曉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.94,0:25:13.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}夜現晨湮之法  …願君得察
